{"tid":1262010,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普三兒子在餐廳被人吐口水","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T14:00:24.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"318d1e9b821ef0c7c7a9d5b93384d83efb485db0","tid":1262010,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2961907/org/25e49ab0be975a4d1a699371942a576d.jpg/XsnBAdm-Z5nFUTo_Eo907CZ1GvSHB0kQVLJeJVSyXiU?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2961907%2Forg%2F25e49ab0be975a4d1a699371942a576d.jpg%2FXsnBAdm-Z5nFUTo_Eo907CZ1GvSHB0kQVLJeJVSyXiU%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c76d621e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據美國有線電視新聞網絡(CNN)報道，美國總統特朗普的兒子埃里克&middot;特朗普(Eric Trump)25日稱，他在芝加哥一家高檔酒吧被一名女員工吐了口唾沫。<br />\n<br />\n埃里克是特朗普與首任妻子的三子、小唐納德&middot;特朗普(Donald Trump Jr.)和伊萬卡&middot;特朗普(Ivanka Trump)的親弟弟。<br />\n<br />\n埃里克事後表示：「這純粹是一個惡心的行為，出自一個明顯有情緒問題的人。」<br />\n<br />\n事後，白宮特勤局人員已對該名女員工進行問話，其後把她釋放。特勤局發言人拒絕就上述事件置評。<br />\n<br />\n對於這起發生在高檔酒吧的事件，埃里克本人雖然沒有透露更多的細節，但卻歸咎於美國民主黨。他指：「對於一個宣揚寬容的政黨來說，這再次表明他們沒有什麽禮貌。有人變態到不得不向某人吐口水，這只強調了一種病態和絕望，以及我們正在取得勝利的事實。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3fc55a8b68456e62be0e41d974774334387a72","tid":1262010,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"間酒吧收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208e3a606a14a9fc7d3cda66e20d03a304c8a40a","tid":1262010,"uid":219369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"屌得好正"},{"pid":"19941c53a7891b05b6f5d2554dea518dd05428ac","tid":1262010,"uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"208e3a606a14a9fc7d3cda66e20d03a304c8a40a","tid":1262010,"uid":219369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"屌得好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a9d5a7d261e4e9d3e4b71229e901b193a8c0af","tid":1262010,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"侵侵做完淡倉未"},{"pid":"123eb2b9ac57871be9c8d2909b863bc8c512154c","tid":1262010,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"我都好想吐口水, 對林奠兩個打把仔"},{"pid":"e594893dc5d2077edae8a74000c4c8bc7d6231ff","tid":1262010,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"123eb2b9ac57871be9c8d2909b863bc8c512154c","tid":1262010,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"我都好想吐口水, 對林奠兩個打把仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"佢哋喺外國呀，無巴打知？"}]}